  "text": "To account for the problem of multicollinearity, we compute correlations between the explanatory variables in both the performance and the asset allocation analysis. This statistical examination shows that governance is highly correlated to pension fund size. This has already been documented by [CITATION_1] , yet to a lesser extent. To avoid distortionary effects stemming from multicollinearity, the variable Ln(Size) was orthogonalised before applied in the regression equation.",
